title: Asics Gel Resolution 9 Tennis Shoes (French Blue/ Pure Gold)
description: The GEL-RESOLUTION 9 Tennis shoe creates advanced stability and cushioning for players who like to control the game from the baseline.​DYNAWALL technology in the midsole now extends into the heel for added stability during lateral movements. It's a functional feature that's effective when you're running covering both sides of the baseline. ​DYNAWRAP technology in the eyestay has been strategically redesigned to apply pressure when extra support is needed. This allows you to experience a locked-in feel when you're making quick transitions.​ Lastly, the full-length outsole and separated heel help produce a more stable landing for quicker recoveries in between shots.

title: Babolat Premura Padel Shoes (Orange Black)
description: The Babolat Jet Premura Padel is one of the most advanced padel shoes on the market. The Ortholite insole remembers the shape of the players foot to deliver the same comfortable fit every time. Finally, the Michelin generative rubber outsole is specifically designed for Padel use.

title: Penn 40 Outdoor Pickleballs
description: The Penn 40 outdoor ball is ideal for tournament play when a softer ball is needed, recreational club play, and coaches giving instruction. title: Diadem Hero Starter Kit Pickleball Paddle (Pack of 2 Paddles & 2 Balls)
description: The DIADEM HERO STARTER KIT is the perfect bundle for the first time pickleball players. The thicker bumper prevents damage during your learning days on the court. At .55 in thick and 8mm honeycomb core, power will be easy to come by. The next pickleball champion starts here.

title: Asics Gel Game 9 Tennis Shoes (Black/Hot Pink)
description:
Both lightweight and flexible, the Asics GEL-GAME 9 Tennis Shoesis versatile for all-court players. Preserving its excellent support properties, our focus this season was to improve the shoe's ventilation and flexibility.
Featuring an open mesh design on the upper to improve airflow and keep feet cool, this shoe is complemented with synthetic leather overlays and a PU (polyurethane) film that offers improved stability when making abrupt transitions.

title: Asics Solution Swift FF Tennis Shoes (White/Antique Red)
description: The Asics SOLUTION SWIFT FF shoe is designed for all-court players covering the net and baseline. It features a flexible sole design that’s functional for multi-directional movements. This shoe’s midsole is formed with FLYTEFOAM cushioning. It’s a lightweight and durable foam that increases shock absorption. Meanwhile, the midfoot’s TWISTRUSS support unit helps you experience quick and confident cuts on court. The shoe’s outsole mirrors the SOLUTION SPEED FF 2 shoe’s sole design. It’s formed with a vertical dash pattern to improve traction on the court.

title: Asics Solution Speed FF2 Tennis Shoes (Antique Red/White)
description: The fastest model in the ASICS tennis range, our Asics Solution Speed FF 2 Tennis Shoe is all about helping players expand their territory on the court. Combining better stability and a more flexible fit, this shoe is a recommended choice for athletes that are looking for quicker accelerations to be ahead of the ball. The Solution Speed FF 2 model features a PU (polyurethane) application on the upper that helps generate better support, flexibility, and an improved fit. Implementing Dynawrap technology into the eye stay, this application helps provide more stability in the forefoot during side-to-side movements. Additionally, the sock liner is produced with a solution dyeing process that reduces water usage by 33% and carbon emissions by approx. 45%. Twisstruss technology in the midsole assists players who are regularly moving from the baseline to the net by improving their cutting motions and quick transitions.

title: Asics Gel Resolution 9 Tennis Shoes (Black/White)
description: The GEL-RESOLUTION 9 Tennis shoe creates advanced stability and cushioning for players who like to control the game from the baseline.​DYNAWALL technology in the midsole now extends into the heel for added stability during lateral movements. It's a functional feature that's effective when you're running covering both sides of the baseline. ​DYNAWRAP technology in the eyestay has been strategically redesigned to apply pressure when extra support is needed. This allows you to experience a locked-in feel when you're making quick transitions.​ Lastly, the full-length outsole and separated heel help produce a more stable landing for quicker recoveries in between shots.

title: Asics GEL-COURTMOV+ Badminton Shoes (Lake Drive/Hazard Green)
description:
Asics GEL-COURT MOV+ shoe is designed for a range of indoor court athletes playing at a competitive level. These athletes are seeking a comfortable and breathable model that's effective for multi-directional movements.

The mesh underlays increase breathability to help keep feet cool, while the no-sew design provides improved flexibility and a more accommodating fit.
GELCOURTMOV+ upper also features a solution that uses less water and inks for a more sustainable manufacturing approach.
Excellent for pivoting thanks to the pivot zone in the outsole, the shoe also features deeper flexion grooves that deliver better flexibility during multi-directional movements and abrupt transitions.
Mesh and no-sew upper improve flexibility & Lateral wrap-up construction improves stability
GELCOURTMOV+ technology cushioning in the forefoot improves shock absorption for a smoother landing.

title: Yonex Osaka Ezone 98 Tennis Racquet
description:
The OSAKA EZONE was designed in collaboration with Naomi Osaka (JPN) and her sister Mari Osaka. The OSAKA EZONE is an added cosmetic to the 7th-generation EZONE series, which is crafted for power and comfort.
ISOMETRIC
7% LARGER SWEET SPOT
Developed over 30 years ago, the ISOMETRIC™ design increases the sweet spot by 7%*. Compared to a conventional round frame, a square-shaped ISOMETRIC™ racquet generates a larger sweet spot by optimizing the intersection of the main and cross strings. ISOMETRIC™ technology delivers greater control without sacrificing power.
LINER TECH
For Improved Power And Comfort
Straight hole grommets elongate the strings to optimize power and comfort on off-center shots.
O.P.S (Oval Pressed Shaft)
First introduced in 1969 with the T-7000 - our first aluminum tennis racquet - the Oval Pressed Shaft (OPS) is still incorporated into our most popular racquet series today. The Oval Pressed Shaft is designed to give players more spin, control, and feel. The shaft flexes at impact, increasing dwell time and minimizing vibrations.
Vibration Dampening Mesh (VDM)
First used in our snowboards to reduce vibrations at impact, Vibration Dampening Mesh (VDM) is now used in four of our racquet series. VDM is a stretchy mesh material that is wrapped around the graphite within the grip to filter unwanted vibrations and improve touch and precision.
2G-Namd Speed
IMPROVED FEEL AND BALL SPEED
A high modulus graphite fibers are bound with a carbon nanotube (CNT) structure, reducing energy loss, which enables to transfer the energy into quick snapback.
AERO SHAPE DESIGN
FOR A PLUSH FEEL
An inverted frame design with a thinner frame face results in a softer racquet.
SHAFT DESIGN
FOR IMPROVED S TABILITY AND POWER
A thicker shaft structure with a convex design reduces unwanted racquet torque on off-centered shots for added power.

ISOMETRIC
Larger Sweet Spot

Among the innovative technologies is HEAD's Adaptive Fan Pattern, which allows you to choose between a straight string pattern for more power or a special fan-shaped pattern for additional control. • Auxetic construction for sensational feel • Slim, aerodynamic shape for ultimate ball control close to the wall• Endorsed by Joelle King and Georgina Kennedy • New, see-through carbon in the shaft for modern look

The lightweight squash racquet includes a major estimated head with a 12 mains x 17 crosses string example to give exact exactness each hit. Most moderateand durable. Playability: The Microgel Blast is an all-rounder that is designed for the power club
Specifications: Head Size - 495 sq.cm / 77 sq.in | Weight - 150 grams | Balance - Head Heavy | String Pattern - 12/17 | Grip Size - 4 0/8 | Beam - 20 mm | Ideal for - Club Players.

title: HEAD Graphene XT Hurricane 12 Squash Racquet (Black)
description:
The latest offer from the Head company. The squash racquet with the new HEAD Graphene XT  technology offers easier swing while generating even more power. Thanks to the use of Graphene XT , it was possible to significantly reduce the weight of the racquet frame, making it highly manoeuvrable.


Playability : This Top End squash racquet for men and women offers great feel and controllable power to Intermediate tournament players.
String pattern : Wider Cross-Strings (Open 12x17 string pattern) for added Power and Spin.
Specifications : Material - Graphite / Graphene XT | Weight (Unstrung) - 123 grams | String Pattern - 12/17 | Head size - 500 sq.cm | Balance – Head Heavy | Grip Size - G3 | Playing Level - Intermediate

title: HEAD G 110 Squash Racquet
description:
HEAD G. 110 Squash Racquet is made with the Titanium and Graphite composition, which provides the racquet with the robust structure without increasing the weight of the racquet. It offers excellent manoeuvrability and power.
The HEAD franchise has integrated Head G. 110 with Intelfibre Technology, which provides the racquet with more stiffness. Intelfibre Technology also helps reduce as much as 20% of the vibration feedback when the ball hits the racquet strings, which ultimately improves the accuracy of the shots.
The HEAD G. 110 has the Power Frame Technology, which delivers firm grip and resilience. Besides, the Head franchise has also incorporated the Head G. 110 racquet with its signature Power Pattern Technology, which not only expands the Sweet Spot but also boosts the power and control of the racquet.

title: HEAD Extreme Junior 2023 Squash Racquet
description: The EXTREME JUNIOR brings all the benefits and technologies of the grown-up EXTREME 120 to the next generation. Made of a lightweight graphite material it provides an improved power transfer thanks to new frame construction and thinner shaft. In addition, the racquet features the Innegra technology, a hybrid-composite structure integrated into the racquet for advanced shock absorption and enhanced stability. It also comes with an entirely new and very bold asymmetric color-blocking design that makes this one easily stand out on every court.

title: HEAD Extreme 135 2023 Squash Racquet
description: With its power and even balance, the teardrop-shaped EXTREME 135 SQUASH RACQUET is an all-rounder that will suit the club player who feels at home on all parts of the court. The 135g frame is durable, with a thin shaft, and constructed for excellent power transfer. The Innegra™ technology, a hybrid-composite structure which is integrated into the racquet, delivers advanced shock absorption and enhanced stability. The EXTREME 135 is offered with a new, modern design with metallic, earthy tones. • Even-balanced frame for the power club player • Excellent power transfer • Innegra™ technology for advanced shock absorption and enhanced stability• New, modern design with metallic, earthy tones

title: HEAD Graphene 360 Speed 125 Squash Racquet
description: The Graphene 360 Speed 125 brings some serious power to the aggressive front court player who needs some additional control. This comes from the slightly higher weight in the racquet head which increases the racquet's overall swing weight for more control. At the same time, the new Graphene 360 technology provides greater stability and optimized energy transfer for more power. The racquet features a power-supporting unique teardrop shape and a bigger head size. It offers HEAD's Adaptive Fan Pattern (AFP) technology that allows you to choose between a straight string pattern for more power or a special fan-shaped pattern for more control. And to top it off, the racquet features a new and very bold asymmetric color-blocking design that will surely turn heads.

title: HEAD Cyber Tour Squash Racquet (Green/Black)
description:
Recreational players can add some power to their games with the CYBER TOUR SQUASH RACQUET, which has been updated with a new, playful design. The lightest racquet in the CYBER series has a teardrop shape and is made with HEAD's Amplified Fibre Technology, which supplies additional power by increasing the stiffness in the frame.

Power for new and casual players
Lightweight with a teardrop shape
Amplified Fibre Technology for additional power
Fresh, playful design

Frame Weight : 160 g
String Pattern : 12/17
Head Size : 500 cm² / 78 in²
Grip Size : 3 7/8
Balance : Head Heavy
Beam: 17,6

title: HEAD Cyber Pro Squash Racquet (Red/Black)
description: With the even balance between control and power, the CYBER PRO SQUASH RACQUET is ideal for an occasional game of squash. Refreshed with a new, playful design, the racquet is slightly heavier than the TOUR model, and has a classic heart shape, for more stability and control. For additional power, the racquet is made with HEAD's Amplified Fibre Technology, which increases the stiffness in the frame. • Control and power for recreational players • Amplified Fibre Technology for additional power • New, playful design

title: HEAD Extreme 120 Squash Racquet
description: With a lightweight, teardrop-shaped frame that supplies stable power, the EXTREME 120 SQUASH RACQUET is designed for the aggressive front-court club player. The 120g frame offers superior power transfer and a thin shaft, as well as Innegra™ technology, a hybrid-composite structure which is integrated into the racquet and delivers advanced shock absorption and enhanced stability. You're assured of making an impact on court with the EXTREME 120, which has a new, modern, black and white design. • Lightweight, teardrop-shaped frame delivers stable power • Ideal for an aggressive, front-court club player• Innegra™ technology for advanced shock absorption and enhanced stability• New, modern, black and white design

title: HEAD Cyber Elite 2022 Squash Racquet
description: If you are new to squash, or you only step on the court occasionally, you will appreciate how easy it is to play with the CYBER ELITE SQUASH RACQUET. Head-light, and heavier than the TOUR and PRO models, this racquet offers the control and stability that you need when you are learning the game. The playful design enhances the appeal of a racquet that is made with HEAD's Amplified Fibre Technology, which enhances stiffness, giving you more power. • Easy to handle and forgiving • Control and stability for new and casual players • Amplified Fibre Technology for additional power • Playful design

title: Head Zephyr UL 2023 Padel Racquet (Red)
description: Weighing a mere 340 grams, the ZEPHYR ULTRA LIGHT is the lightest model in the ZEPHYR range, and one of the lightest padel racquets on the market. Comfortable and easy to play with, this racquet is ideal for younger players who are moving from a junior to an adult model, but it is versatile and will also suit men and women. The introduction of Graphene 360+ technology improves the flex and feel of the ZEPHYR ULTRA LIGHT, while the Power Foam adds comfort and helps with off-center shots. With its fresh new design, this racquet will appeal to both sexes.

description: Supercharge your game with the Head FLASH 2023 Padel Racquet, an oversized, teardrop-shaped all-rounder. While the fiberglass hitting surface supplies a softer feel and touch, the larger sweetspot offers more tolerance and forgiveness. And you will look the part on court as the FLASH has been refreshed with a new design which includes color pops.

title: Asics Gel Rocket 11 (Blue) Badminton Shoes
description: The Asics Gel Rocket 11 Badminton shoes is a multi-purpose indoor court shoe that comes with excellent cushioning. Designed with a TRUSSTIC application in the midsole, this application improves stability during quick transitions. Creating excellent comfort, the GEL technology cushioning unit in the heel is functional for providing better shock absorption. A wrap-up outsole and outrigger are functional support components during side-to-side movements. In contrast, the heel wrap-up expands the contact area during the landing phase of your stride to help generate a smoother landing. Lastly, the flexible grooves in the outsole complement a side grip design that improves flexibility on the court.

title: Head Graphene 360+ Speed MP Lite Tennis Racquet
description:
The Head 360+ Speed MP Lite Tennis Racquet is slightly lighter than the PRO and provides the silo’s characteristics in an easier-to-handle version for many players.
It comes with the Graphene 360+ technology, a combination of Graphene 360’s energy transfer and innovative spiral fibers for enhanced flex and clean impact feel as well as a 16/19 string pattern for an enhanced spin during fast rallies. It not only feels more solid against big-hitting opponents but also does a better job driving the ball through the court. It also gives enough spin potential to bring the ball down hard.
The tennis racquet is available in a new design with an asymmetric combination of matte, glossy white, and glossy black.

title: Head Graphene 360+ Speed Pro Tennis Racquet
description:
The Head Graphene 360+ Speed Pro Tennis Racquet comes with the Graphene 360+ technology, a combination of Graphene 360’s energy transfer and innovative spiral fibers for enhanced flex and clean impact feel as well as a 16/19 string pattern for an enhanced spin during fast rallies.
It not only feels more solid against big-hitting opponents, but it also does a better job driving the ball through the court. It also gives enough spin potential to bring the ball down hard. The Speed Pro is available in a new design with an asymmetric combination of matte, glossy white, and glossy black.

title: Head Radical Pro Tennis Racquet
description:
The Head Radical Pro Tennis Racquet is manufactured in China and has a graphite and graphene 360+ composition. The racquet's head size is 98 square inches and its length is 27 inches.
Key Features: GRAPHENE 360+ : GRAPHENE 360+ is the combination of HEAD’s signature Graphene 360 technology for optimized energy transfer and the innovative spiral fibers for enhanced flex and clean impact feel.
CONTROL PATTERN : A more dense 16/19 string pattern provides the perfect mix of control and power.
SOUND GROMMETS: Sound grommets provide enhanced power via greater string movement and optimize sound and vibrations
VARIABLE BEAM : The variable beam cross-section perfectly balances the power, control and spin of the racquet.

title: Head Radical MP Tennis Racquet
description:
The Head Radical MP Tennis Racquet is a powerful tennis racquet with excellent feel and spin-friendly control. With the Graphene 360+ technology, and a fresh, vibrant design, the RADICAL MP is made for the all-court tournament player seeking the perfect blend of power and handling. Slightly lighter than its bigger brother the RADICAL PRO, the RADICAL MP is designed for the versatile all-court tournament player, with a perfect blend of power, control and spin. Along with a fresh, vibrant and daring design that illustrates its modernity, and a new frame for improved playability, the racquet has also been upgraded with the Graphene 360+ technology for enhanced flex and clean impact feel.
Key Features: GRAPHENE 360+ : GRAPHENE 360+ is the combination of HEAD’s signature Graphene 360 technology for optimized energy transfer and the innovative spiral fibers for enhanced flex and clean impact feel.
CONTROL PATTERN : A more dense 16/19 string pattern provides the perfect mix of control and power.
SOUND GROMMETS: Sound grommets provide enhanced power via greater string movement and optimize sound and vibrations
VARIABLE BEAM : The variable beam cross-section perfectly balances the power, control and spin of the racquet.

title: Head Boom Team L 2022 Tennis Racquet
description:
The Head Boom Team L 2022 Tennis Racquet is manufactured in China and has a graphite composition. The racquet's head size is 98 square inches and its length is 27 inches.
Key Features: AUXETIC : Auxetic constructions show a unique deformation compared to non-Auxetic constructions. Due to their internal properties, Auxetic constructions widen when a “pull” force is applied and contract when squeezed. The bigger the applied force, the bigger the Auxetic reaction.
UNI PATTERN : The specially designed uniform string pattern allows for a consistent ball trajectory on every shot for reliable and forgiving play.
DIRECTIONAL DRILLING : Directional drilling combine increased power and sweetspot, delivering a plush impact feel.
GRAPHENE INSIDE : Strategically positioned in most of our racquets, Graphene strengthens the frame, provides greater stability and optimises energy transfer from racquet to ball. When you buy your next racquet, be sure it has GRAPHENE INSIDE.
MORPH BEAM : The unique frame construction merges an elongated box beam shaft with a powerful head for the perfect blend of feel and ease on court.
POWER GROMMETS : The enlarged power grommets maximize string movement for increased power.

title: Babolat Pure Drive Team Tennis Racquet
weight: ELLIPTIC FRAME : Elliptical frame structure of the Babolat Pure Drive Team Tennis Racquet comes with optimal resistance and overall rigidity which provides phenomenal power.
description:
The Babolat Pure Drive Team Tennis Racquet offers the spin, power, and precision of the standard Pure Drive but in a slightly lighter, more manageable package. At 10.7 ounces strung and boasting a 316RDC swing weight, the Pure Drive Team is perfectly weighted for the intermediate player who craves speed but also wants moderate plow-through for battling against higher levels of pace.
Key Features: HTR SYSTEM : The High Torsional Rigidity (HTR) system is a new lay-up composition in the hoop of the Babolat Pure Drive Team Tennis Racquet for increased rigidity to produce explosive winners at will.
SWX PURE FEEL : New technology featuring extended wrapping of SMAC technology, the cutting-edge vibration filtration system integrated into the lay-up composition, provides an unrivaled feel at ball impact and a unique sound on every shot.
ELLIPTIC FRAME : Elliptical frame structure of the Babolat Pure Drive Team Tennis Racquet comes with optimal resistance and overall rigidity which provides phenomenal power.

title: Babolat Pure Aero RAFA Team Tennis Racquet
description:
The Babolat Pure Aero RAFA Team Tennis Racquet is one of the most well-known and light tennis racquets ever produced. This racket is ideal for intermediate and advanced players seeking for a fast spin-monster with precision targeting. It also has the spin-friendly accuracy and sheer power that makes it deadly in the hands of aggressive players.
Key Features: AEROMODULAR 3 : An aerodynamic frame integrating the bumper and grommets increases your racquet head speed and spin generation.
WOOFER SYSTEM : It provides maximum spin with great feeling and superior control.
CORTEX PURE FEEL POWERED BY SMAC : Better vibration dampening thanks to a new material integrated in the graphite of the racquet that provides pure feel with an incredible sound.

title: Babolat Pure Aero 2023 Tennis Racquet
description:
The Babolat Pure Aero 2023 Tennis Racket is one of the most well-known and powerful tennis rackets. It also has the spin-friendly accuracy and sheer power that makes it deadly in the hands of aggressive players. The racket is ideal for intermediate and advanced players seeking for a fast spin-monster with precision targeting.
Key Features: NF²-TECH : Flax inserts at strategic locations in the frame create optimal shock absorption and sound quality for an exceptional playing experience.
FSI SPIN TECHNOLOGY : A new string pattern featuring spin grommets positioned at the top and bottom of the racquet head enables the strings to move more freely creating greater spin. The Woofer system increases the contact time between the ball and strings for improved feel and more control.
AEROMODULAR 3 : An aerodynamic frame integrating the bumper and grommets increases Babolat Pure Aero 2023 Tennis Racquet head speed and spin generation.

title: Mizuno Speed Flex 9.1 Badminton Racket
description:
Mizuno's Speed Flex 9.1 badminton Racket is perfect for advance level players. With an even balance, the Racket weighs just 83 grams and has a stringing capacity of 30 lbs.
Slim Aerodynamic Frame: Slim Aerodynamic Frame profile significantly reduces the amount of drag and maximizes Racket head speed impact.
Tapered Shaft: A revolutionary shaft construction of Mizuno Speedlfix 9.1 Badminton Racket, it is tapered down from 7.5mm at the top cap to 6.5mm at the T-Joint, allowing great flex on impact, minimizing shock to the wrist and has twice the force of restoration than the average shaft, resulting in superior resiliency, generating higher repulsion power and shuttlecock return speed.
Hot Melt Tech: The graphite sheets are heated at a higher temperature further to eliminate the impurities during the initial manufacturing process. This results in a smoother, more consistent coating that not only strengthens the frame but enhances the aerodynamics of the graphite, thus increasing the Mizuno Speedlfex 9.1 Badminton Racket’s velocity.

title: Mizuno JPX Limited Edition Attack Badminton Racket
description:
The Mizuno JPX Limited Edition Attack badminton Racquet has a head-heavy balance and is a perfect badminton for advance level players. The badminton Racquet weighs just 85 grams and has a stringing capacity of 30 lbs.
Key Features
Aero Hexagram: The six-pointed ‘star-like’ frame with equilateral angles reduces air resistance, and the lower frame’s high-level strength increases repulsion power. The aerodynamic frame is perfect for lightning-fast shots and high-speed rallies
3D Power Matrix: The unique manufacturing process of interlinking and overlapping composite fibers that are woven over the frame creates a highly resilient design. This seamless construction evenly dissipates the pressure that a racquet receives during aggressive play and protects the underlying structure of the frame.
Hot Melt Tech: The graphite sheets are heated at a higher temperature to further eliminate the impurities during the initial manufacturing process. This results in a smoother, more consistent coating that strengthens the frame and enhances the graphite's aerodynamics, thus increasing the racquet's velocity.
CombiFrame: The CombiFrame infuses two distinctive features resulting in a uniquely versatile frame. Contouring from an Aero Hexagram frame starting at the bridge to a Box Frame from the middle to the top of the racquet. This combination generates highly explosive head speed, extreme power, and unswerving control.
Rapid Response System: The Rapid Response System is an innovative technology that delivers explosive power with every shot. By carefully calibrating the kick-point on the shaft, a moderate snapping back and a quick spring back create a faster and more accurate smash.
Nano PEF: The shaft is constructed using ‘Nano PEF’ (Nano Polyethylene Fibre), which is light enough to float on water yet able to withstand immense forces. These characteristics allow for maximum shock absorption. Mizuno badminton Racquets are considered to be one of the best in the industry. title: Li-Ning Aeronaut 8000 Unstrung Badminton Racket
description:
Li-Ning Aeronaut series is specially designed for players looking for great control in his/her badminton racquet without any compromise in the racquet's power. The Aeronaut series badminton racquet has a unique air stream channel integrated into the racquet’s head, so this air stream channel minimizes the air resistance, which produces faster shuttlecock speed.
The Aeronaut 8000 Badminton Racquet shaft is also made from military-grade carbon fiber. This medium flex shaft is designed for the rapid repulsion power that helps fast players for switching between offense and defense. This shaft also provides great control.
Technologies used in this racquet:
1. Wing Stabilizer: Wing Stabilizer is a unique technology used in aviation to control unnecessary vibration. Li Ning used this technology to control the Racquet frame resulting in the racquet absorbing unnecessary shaking from the vibrations and restoring the racquet’s outer “wings” back to a precision performance mode.
2. MPCF Reinforcing Technology: Li-Ning takes up racquet production to a new level & reduces the chances of imperfections. Li-Ning implements multi-layer carbon fibers for strength and durability.
3. Dynamic Optimum Frame: All the Badminton Racquets have a Dynamic Optimum Frame means they have a more prominent extended sweet spot, so the hitting point is moved higher & provides a larger defensive area.
4. Aerotec Beam System: By collecting the data from the courts & analyzing them, Li-Ning manufactures the most aerodynamic racquet. This results in extremely low drag & high intensity.
5. Stabilized Torsion Control: In this technology, we design shots that are not hit with the sweet spot to act almost like they hit the sweet spot. This technology allows the frame to remain stabilized for an even-hitting surface.
6. TB Nano: Nano Technology combines carbon fiber & resin more closely. This process gives better elasticity, stability, and durability overall; we say the more powerful striking.
About Li-Ning: Li-Ning Company Limited is a Chinese sportswear and sports equipment company founded by former Olympic gymnast Li Ning. The company endorses a number of athletes and teams worldwide.
 Is the racket unstrung?
Yes, the Li-Ning Aeronaut 8000 Unstrung Badminton Racket is an unstrung badminton racket.

title: Li-Ning Turbo Charging 70 Badminton Racket
description:
Li-Ning Turbo Charging 70 Badminton Racket is a head-heavy frame with a stiff shaft and an elastic head design. It is ideal for quick players with rapid attacks and strong defensive skills.
It is built on the Turbo Charging Technology Platform that is designed for aerodynamic efficiency. It features an innovative trapezoidal frame construction that energizes the player with extra strong swing speeds and fast reaction times.
The Li-Ning DRIVE Series badminton racquets feature a stiffer shaft and highly elastic head design with rapid repulsion power. Suitable for fast players that are skilled in switching quickly between offense and defense.
The Turbo Charging Technology Platform uses a 2-digit numbering system. The first digit determines the grade of the racquet as follows:
If the first digit is 1, 2 or 3, the racquet is suitable for beginners. If the first digit is 4, 5 or 6, the racquet is suitable for intermediate players. If the first digit is 7, 8 or 9, the racquet is suitable for advanced players,
Technologies used in the racket:
Wing Stabilizer: Introducing aviation technology to control the Racquet frame. After impact, Li-Ning racquets absorb unnecessary shaking from vibrations and restore the racquet’s outer “wings” back to a precision performance mode. This readies the player for a quick, precise, and stable follow-up stroke.
MPCF Reinforcing Technology: Li-Ning takes the extra step to avoid imperfections sometimes caused by machine processing of other racquets. The racquet is crafted with strength and longevity by implementing multi-layer carbon fibers.
Dynamic-Optimum Frame: Li-Ning racquets are manufactured with a sweet spot that extends upward. The hitting point is moved higher, providing a larger defensive area. This considerably improves hitting velocity due to a wider stringed area and increased bounce strength.
Aerotec-Beam System: Implementing real data compiled from the field, Li-Ning manufactures the most aerodynamic Racquets possible. Advanced calculations have resulted in Racquets with extremely low drag and higher intensity.
TB Nano: The nanometer technology combines carbon fiber and resin more closely. This method provides better elasticity, stability, and durability – resulting in more powerful striking.
Stabilized Elastic Shaft: We filled the slim shafts of our racquets with the same aramid fibers found in body armor and helmets. These heat-resistant and strong synthetic fibers provide world-class flexibility and durability. This is another way Li-Ning helps avoid sports injuries.
Hot Melt: Our proprietary process thoroughly mixes resins with carbon fibers to ensure all our racquets are manufactured in a uniform manner. This provides optimum strength and consistent performance no matter which Racquet you choose.
Stabilized Torsion Angle: With a Stabilized Torsion Angle, shots that are not hit with the sweet spot of the Racquet are designed to act almost as if they were. This torsion resistance performance allows the frame to stabilize for an even-hitting surface.
FRTP Tech: By changing the shaft’s recoil point, our racquets quickly bend and rebound back into position, so you are ready for the continuous volley and attack.
About Li-Ning: Li-Ning Company Limited is a Chinese sportswear and sports equipment company founded by former Olympic gymnast Li Ning. The company endorses a number of athletes and teams worldwide.
 Is the racket suitable for aggressive players?
Yes, the Li-Ning Turbo Charging 70 Badminton Racket is perfectly suited for fast-paced gameplay and aggressive players.

title: MuscleTech Masstech Extreme 2000 - Weight Gainer
description:
Mass-Tech Extreme 2000 is a mass gainer protein powder designed for individuals aiming to gain extreme mass and build muscle. Here are some key features and benefits of Mass-Tech Extreme 2000:


5-in-1 Hardcore Mass Gainer: This product is formulated to assist individuals in putting on extreme mass. It offers a comprehensive approach to muscle building.


High Protein Content: With 30g of premium protein per serving, Mass-Tech Extreme 2000 provides ample protein to support muscle growth and recovery.


Superior Weight Gainer: Compared to other mass gainers, Mass-Tech Extreme 2000 delivers more protein, better calories, and promises bigger results. It provides the necessary macronutrients for quality mass gain.


Creatine Monohydrate: This supplement contains a clinically validated dose of 1.5g of creatine monohydrate per serving. Creatine helps increase strength and aids in the regeneration of ATP stores depleted during resistance training.


Daily Usage: It is recommended to mix one serving of Mass-Tech Extreme 2000 with 20 oz of water or skim milk in a blender and consume it once daily. It can be taken in the morning, between meals, or post-workout to support muscle growth and recovery.


It's important to note that while Mass-Tech Extreme 2000 can be a valuable tool for individuals looking to build muscle and gain mass, it should be used as part of a balanced diet and exercise program. Additionally, individuals should consult with a healthcare professional before starting any new supplement regimen, especially if they have any underlying health conditions or concerns.

title: Muscle Tech Performance Series Nitro-Tech Ripped Vanilla Bean
description:
MuscleTech Nitro-Tech Ripped is a high-quality whey protein supplement specifically formulated to support lean muscle building and weight loss efforts. Here are some key features and benefits of Nitro-Tech Ripped:


Lean Muscle Building: Each serving provides 30g of premium whey protein, primarily sourced from whey protein peptides and whey protein isolate. This high protein content supports muscle repair and growth, crucial for individuals aiming to build lean muscle mass.


Ripped Body Formula: Nitro-Tech Ripped features a unique blend of ingredients designed to aid in weight loss and improve performance. These ingredients include C. canephora robusta, L-carnitine L-tartrate (500mg), CLA (250mg), rosehip extract, and MCT oil. These components are known for their potential to assist in weight management, reduce fatigue, and enhance muscle growth. Importantly, the formula is caffeine and stimulant-free, making it suitable for athletes and individuals sensitive to stimulants.


Miscibility & Digestibility: Nitro-Tech Ripped undergoes a multi-phase filtration process to ensure high purity and easy mixability with water or other liquids. This enhances its absorption into the body, allowing for faster delivery of nutrients to muscles for optimal recovery and growth.


The Perfect Taste: Available in two unique flavors, MuscleTech Nitro-Tech Ripped offers a delicious taste experience. Formulated with a blend of artificial and natural flavors, it provides a gourmet kick to your workouts, making it easier and more enjoyable to incorporate into your daily routine.


Overall, MuscleTech Nitro-Tech Ripped is a versatile protein supplement suitable for individuals looking to build lean muscle mass, support weight loss efforts, and enhance overall performance. It offers a convenient and delicious way to meet protein needs while providing additional benefits for those striving to achieve their fitness goals.

title: MuscleTech Hydroxycut Hardcore Super Elite
description:
TRUSTED SCIENCE-BACKED INGREDIENTS For over 20 years, Hydroxycut® has been a go-to choice for countless individuals striving towards their goals. Hydroxycut® Hardcore Super Elite, our most potent formula yet, boasts a multi-ingredient complex for a unique sensory experience.
SCIENCE-SUPPORTED WEIGHT MANAGEMENT In two double-blind, placebo-controlled trials, C. canephora robusta extract aided in weight management. One study spanned 60 days with both groups adhering to a low-calorie diet. The second trial, lasting 8 weeks, involved a calorie-restricted diet and moderate exercise regimen for both groups.
CAFFEINE FOR ALERTNESS Caffeine enhances alertness and concentration. Its benefits are realized with a dose of 3mg/kg body weight taken at least one hour before exercise, provided other caffeine intake is avoided for 24 hours before product consumption in habitual caffeine users.
CHOLINE FOR METABOLISM Choline supports normal lipid metabolism
 
How to Use?To gauge tolerance, begin with 1 capsule daily on the first day. Increase to 2 capsules daily on days 2 and 3. From day 4 onwards, take 2 capsules twice daily, 30 to 60 minutes before your two main meals, such as breakfast and lunch.

title: Asics Court FF3 Novak Tennis Shoes(Cranberry/ White)
model: For a smoother crossover step, this shoe allows you to perform quicker turns in a shorter timeframe. With good outsole grip and a TWISTRUSS™ support system, you can push off the ground with<Truncated>
description:
The Asics COURT FF 3 tennis shoe is modeled after Novak Djokovic’s playing style. These shoes are designed to help you swing stronger and recover quicker between shots.
Novak has a zero-step shot. This means that he’s swinging his racquet when he lands. By increasing the outsole’s contact area, the shoe creates a stable landing and reduces the load placed on the body. As a result, you’re able to put more energy into generating a powerful swing.
For a smoother crossover step, this shoe allows you to perform quicker turns in a shorter timeframe. With good outsole grip and a TWISTRUSS™ support system, you can push off the ground with more force. This helps you quickly recover and get back to your ready position more smoothly.

title: Babolat Premura 2 Padel Shoes (Black/Fista Red)
description: The Babolat Jet Premura Padel is one of the most advanced padel shoes on the market. Designed for advanced padel players, the Matryx SL technology in the one-piece upper was developed by experts in high performance technical fabrics, and is designed to meet the specific needs of padel players by using Kevlar and Polyamide fibers woven into targeted areas for ultimate support. A 360 degree flex wrap around proves flexible durability on the side of the foot for the most aggressive movers. The Ortholite insole remembers the shape of the players foot to deliver the same comfortable fit every time. Finally, the Michelin generative rubber outsole is specifically designed for Padel use.

title: Asics Gel Resolution 9 Tennis Shoes (White)
description: The GEL-RESOLUTION 9 Tennis shoe creates advanced stability and cushioning for players who like to control the game from the baseline.​DYNAWALL technology in the midsole now extends into the heel for added stability during lateral movements. It's a functional feature that's effective when you're running covering both sides of the baseline. ​DYNAWRAP technology in the eyestay has been strategically redesigned to apply pressure when extra support is needed. This allows you to experience a locked-in feel when you're making quick transitions.​ Lastly, the full-length outsole and separated heel help produce a more stable landing for quicker recoveries in between shots.

title: Asics Solution Speed FF2Tennis Shoes (White/Restful Teal)
description: The fastest model in the ASICS tennis range, our Asics Solution Speed FF 2 Tennis Shoe is all about helping players expand their territory on the court. Combining better stability and a more flexible fit, this shoe is a recommended choice for athletes that are looking for quicker accelerations to be ahead of the ball. The Solution Speed FF 2 model features a PU (polyurethane) application on the upper that helps generate better support, flexibility, and an improved fit. Implementing Dynawrap technology into the eye stay, this application helps provide more stability in the forefoot during side-to-side movements. Additionally, the sock liner is produced with a solution dyeing process that reduces water usage by 33% and carbon emissions by approx. 45%. Twisstruss technology in the midsole assists players who are regularly moving from the baseline to the net by improving their cutting motions and quick transitions.

title: Asics Solution Swift FF Tennis Shoes (Black/Hot Pink)
description: The Asics SOLUTION SWIFT FF shoe is designed for all-court players covering the net and baseline. It features a flexible sole design that’s functional for multi-directional movements. Meanwhile, the midfoot’s TWISTRUSS support unit helps you experience quick and confident cuts on court. The shoe’s outsole mirrors the SOLUTION SPEED FF 2 shoe’s sole design. It’s formed with a vertical dash pattern to improve traction on the court.

title: Asics Gel Resolution 9 Tennis Shoes (Steel Blue/Hazard Green)
description: The GEL-RESOLUTION 9 Tennis shoe creates advanced stability and cushioning for players who like to control the game from the baseline.​DYNAWALL technology in the midsole now extends into the heel for added stability during lateral movements. It's a functional feature that's effective when you're running covering both sides of the baseline. ​DYNAWRAP technology in the eyestay has been strategically redesigned to apply pressure when extra support is needed. This allows you to experience a locked-in feel when you're making quick transitions.​ Lastly, the full-length outsole and separated heel help produce a more stable landing for quicker recoveries in between shots.

description:
The Asics COURT FF 3 tennis shoe is modeled after Novak Djokovic’s playing style. These shoes are designed to help you swing stronger and recover quicker between shots.
Novak has a zero-step shot. This means that he’s swinging his racquet when he lands. By increasing the outsole’s contact area, the shoe creates a stable landing and reduces the load placed on the body. As a result, you’re able to put more energy into generating a powerful swing.
For a smoother crossover step, this shoe allows you to perform quicker turns in a shorter timeframe. With good outsole grip and a TWISTRUSS™ support system, you can push off the ground with more force. This helps you quickly recover and get back to your ready position more smoothly.

title: Yonex Percept 100L Tennis Racquet
description:
ISOMETRIC
7% LARGER SWEET SPOT
Developed over 30 years ago, the ISOMETRIC™ design increases the sweet spot by 7%*.
Compared to a conventional round frame, a square-shaped ISOMETRIC™ racquet generates a larger sweet spot by optimizing the intersection of the main and cross strings.
ISOMETRIC™ technology delivers greater control without sacrificing power.
SERVO FILTER
PROPERTIES:
A transparent film placed between graphite enhances flexibility when pressure is applied and filters out unnecessary vibration.
RESULT:
60%* more flexible and 500%* faster vibration dampening than graphite
FLEXCON SYSTEM＋2G-NAMD™ FLEX FORCE
FLEXCON SYSTEM
PROPERTIES:
 
A tapered and elongated box frame shaft is composed with 2G-Namd™ Flex Force and SERVO FILTER. This system helps the racquet to flex and extend the ball pocketing duration at the impact.
RESULT:
15%* more flexibility on the racquet shaft
2G-NAMD™ FLEX FORCE
Flex Force graphite allows the racquet to quickly flex and snap back for greater spin and faster ball acceleration off the string bed.
STIFF RACQUET FACE DESIGN
PROPERTIES:
Increase the graphite content of the racquet face. This improves ball control by stabilizing the racquet face at impact.
RESULT:
3%* more stability on the racquet face

title: Yonex VCORE 100L Tennis Racquet (Scarlet)
description:
ISOMETRIC
7% LARGER SWEET SPOT
Developed over 30 years ago, the ISOMETRIC™ design increases the sweet spot by 7%*.
Compared to a conventional round frame, a square-shaped ISOMETRIC™ racquet generates a larger sweet spot by optimizing the intersection of the main and cross strings. ISOMETRIC™ technology delivers greater control without sacrificing power.
Aero Fin Technology
Improved Maneuvering
Aerodynamic fins that were featured in the VCORE SV have also been upgraded and positioned towards the bottom of the VCORE’s frame. The new Aero Fins are strategically carved out sections that allow for improved maneuverability.
Aero Trench
Reduced Drag
To achieve faster head speeds for increased spin potential, the new Aero Trench reduces drag by uniquely hiding the grommets located at the top of the racquet frame.
LINER TECH
For Maximum Spin Potential
Newly engineered straight hole grommets allow more string movement on off-centered shots.
AERO DYNAMIC TECHNOLOGY
Aero Trench and Aero Fin Technology reduce air resistance for easy maneuverability and added spin.
2G-NAMD™ FLEX FORCE
FOR AGGRESSIVE, ATTACKING SPIN Incorporated in the upper throat to the lower frame, new Flex Force graphite allows for the racquet to quickly flex and snapback for maximum spin potential.
SILICONE OIL INFUSED GROMMET
New silicone oil infused within the grommet allows the racquet to quickly flex and snapback into its original position.
String Sync Grommets
FOR BALL BITE AND SPIN
A thin grommet nozzle is inserted into a larger frame hole allowing the string to move together with the grommet for faster snapback.
ENLARGED FRAME TOP
A wider frame at 2 o’clock & 10 o’clock position increases the ball contact area, which produces a higher launch angle.
NEW THROAT DESIGN
Area 2 is H shaped cross section
This “torsional resistance” helps stabilize the racquet, reducing power loss.
Super Cushion Grip

title: Yonex Osaka Ezone 100 Tennis Racquet
description:
The OSAKA EZONE was designed in collaboration with Naomi Osaka (JPN) and her sister Mari Osaka. The OSAKA EZONE is an added cosmetic to the 7th-generation EZONE series, which is crafted for power and comfort.
ISOMETRIC
7% LARGER SWEET SPOT
Developed over 30 years ago, the ISOMETRIC™ design increases the sweet spot by 7%*. Compared to a conventional round frame, a square-shaped ISOMETRIC™ racquet generates a larger sweet spot by optimizing the intersection of the main and cross strings. ISOMETRIC™ technology delivers greater control without sacrificing power.
LINER TECH
For Improved Power And Comfort
Straight hole grommets elongate the strings to optimize power and comfort on off-center shots.
O.P.S (Oval Pressed Shaft)
First introduced in 1969 with the T-7000 - our first aluminum tennis racquet - the Oval Pressed Shaft (OPS) is still incorporated into our most popular racquet series today. The Oval Pressed Shaft is designed to give players more spin, control, and feel. The shaft flexes at impact, increasing dwell time and minimizing vibrations.
Vibration Dampening Mesh (VDM)
First used in our snowboards to reduce vibrations at impact, Vibration Dampening Mesh (VDM) is now used in four of our racquet series. VDM is a stretchy mesh material that is wrapped around the graphite within the grip to filter unwanted vibrations and improve touch and precision.
2G-Namd Speed
IMPROVED FEEL AND BALL SPEED
A high modulus graphite fibers are bound with a carbon nanotube (CNT) structure, reducing energy loss, which enables to transfer the energy into quick snapback.
AERO SHAPE DESIGN
FOR A PLUSH FEEL
An inverted frame design with a thinner frame face results in a softer racquet.
SHAFT DESIGN
FOR IMPROVED S TABILITY AND POWER
A thicker shaft structure with a convex design reduces unwanted racquet torque on off-centered shots for added power.

title: Yonex Ezone 98 Tour Tennis Racquet
description:
Yonex Ezone 98 Tour delivers an excellent plough through efficiency, which enhances the speed of the racquet. The racquet weighs 315 grams and comes with a head size of 98 square inches.
The Yonex Ezone 98 Tour possesses a flexible frame that helps the racquet generate more power. The structure of the Ezone 98 Tour is built with the High Modulus Graphite composite. Yonex has also implanted Ezone 98 Tour with M40X Technology in the throat of the racquet, which provides it with maximum stability.
The Yonex Ezone Tour 98 is further equipped Liner Tech feature that helps the racquet deliver enhanced power and excellent comfort. Yonex has mounted straight hole grommets in the Ezone Tour 98, which extend the strings of the racquet. As a result, Yonex E Zone Tour 98 offers optimised power and comfortable feel even when hitting the off-centred strokes.
Furthermore, Yonex E Zone 98 Tour delivers high precision and shock wave absorption efficiency to improve the performance of the players on the court. The Yonex E Zone Tour racquet has a balance point of 320 mm and stringing pattern of 16 X 19. The racquet possesses a standard length of 27 inches, which is ideal for adult tennis players.

title: HEAD Microgel 125 Squash Racquet
description:
Rock-solid feel and touch, With the lowest density of any material, HEAD Microgel is a revolutionary new silicone-based material. Playability: The Microgel 125 is an all-rounder that is designed for the power club

title: HEAD Graphene 360 Speed 110 Squash Racquet
description: The HEAD Graphene 360 Speed 110, lightest of 360 series brings some serious power to the aggressive front court player who needs some additional control. This comes from the slightly higher weight in the racquet head which increases the racquet's overall swing weight for more control. At the same time, the new Graphene 360 technology provides greater stability and optimized energy transfer for more power. Recommended by Saurav Ghosal, the racquet features a power-supporting unique teardrop shape and a bigger head size. It also offers the revolutionary Corrugated Technology (CT2) which incorporates extra-long corrugated rails in the racquet's shaft for additional stiffness as well as HEAD's Adaptive Fan Pattern (AFP) technology that allows you to choose between a straight string patternfor more power or a special fan-shaped pattern for more control. And to top it off, the racquet features a new and very bold asymmetric color-blocking design that will surely turn heads.

title: HEAD GRAPHENE 360+ Speed 120 Squash Racquet
description:
HEAD Graphene 360+ Speed 120 Squash Racquet Specifications:


Playability: Blend of speed and power for the modern squash player | The perfect racket for the attacking front-court player who is seeking more touch.

Specifications: Head Size - 500 sq.cm / 78 sq.in | Weight - 120 grams / 4.2 oz. | Balance - Head Heavy | String Pattern - 12/17, 16/17 | Grip Size - 3 7/8 | Beam - 20 mm | Ideal for - Tournament Players.

HEAD Graphene 360+ Speed 120 Squash Racquet Technology:


Graphene 360+ Technology: Forms the structural base of the racquet, positioned in the shaft and extending into the racquet head, strengthens the frame, providing greater stability and optimized energy transfer from racquet to ball.



Adaptive Fan Pattern (AFP) : HEAD's well known Adaptive Fan Pattern technology gives you the unique ability to adjust the performance of your racquet without changing the grommets. Choose between the straight pattern to maximize powerand the fan pattern to optimize your control.


Octagonal Power Technology: HEAD's engineers have implemented the new octagonal power Technology into staff of the racquet which features more power and a solid feel through the octagonal shape of the construction.

Stringbed X-Tension: The groove in the upper part of the frame enlarges the space where the strings are able to move during ball contact. This enables an extended use of the trampoline effect and creates more acceleration. It gives you the extra power and ball speed you need to excel in your game.

HEAD Graphene 360+ Speed 120 Squash Racquet Description:
Saurav Ghosal endorses this racquet, which has a teardrop shape that allows for extra power, as well as a fresh, bold and modern design.
 The perfect racquet for the attacking front-court player who is seeking more touch, the Graphene 360+ Speed 120 is engineered with a new mold and some of HEAD's pioneering technologies. Along with the Octagonal Power Technology in the shaft that improves playability, the ultra-modern 120g frame comes with Stringbed X-Tension Technology which increases rebound for additional power.
For even more power, the racquet also now has Graphene 360+ technology, a combination of Graphene 360's energy transfer and innovative spiralfibers which supply enhanced flexand clean impact feel. Among the other technologies is HEAD's Adaptive Fan Pattern, which allows you to choose between a straight string pattern for more power or a special fan-shaped pattern for enhanced control.

title: Asics Blade FF (Black/Safety Yellow) Badminton Shoes
description:
The Asics Blade FF 3 badminton shoe is an excellent choice for badminton players engaging in long rallies with a high jump and smash style of play.
Designed to improve lateral support, this shoe also increases flexibility to accommodate quick multi-directional movements. An improved fit around the ankle helps players quickly shift directions, while the loop system in the eyelets increases midfoot support.
Functional during multi-directional movements, the lateral wrap-up outsole is paired with flex grooves in the outsole to offer excellent stability and flexibility on the court. Thanks to the upper PU (polyurethane) construction, this application offers a better fit with more support and flexibility.
Additionally, the Pguard technology in the medial forefoot increases durability and keeps the shoe from creating too much friction with the court. Paired with Gel technology cushioning and a Flytefoam midsole material to increase shock absorption, the Court Control FF 2 shoe is a recommended model for competitive badminton players with a baseline to net playing style.
About Asics: Asics is a Japanese multinational corporation that produces sportswear. The name is an acronym for the Latin phrase anima sana in corpore sano. Products manufactured and marketed by Asics include footwear, clothing, and accessories.
Are the badminton shoes suited for long rallies?
Yes, being very light on feet, the shoes are perfect for players who like to play long rallies.

title: Asics Court Control FF2 Badminton Shoes
description:
The Asics Court Control FF 2 badminton shoe is an excellent choice for badminton players engaging in long rallies with a high jump and smash style of play.
Designed to improve lateral support, this shoe also increases flexibility to accommodate quick multi-directional movements. An improved fit around the ankle helps players quickly shift directions, while the loop system in the eyelets increases midfoot support.
Functional during multi-directional movements, the lateral wrap-up outsole is paired with flex grooves in the outsole to offer excellent stability and flexibility on the court. Thanks to the upper PU (polyurethane) construction, this application offers a better fit with more support and flexibility.
Additionally, the Pguard technology in the medial forefoot increases durability and keeps the shoe from creating too much friction with the court. Paired with Gel technology cushioning and a Flytefoam midsole material to increase shock absorption, the Court Control FF 2 shoe is a recommended model for competitive badminton players with a baseline to net playing style.
About Asics: Asics is a Japanese multinational corporation that produces sportswear. The name is an acronym for the Latin phrase anima sana in corpore sano. Products manufactured and marketed by Asics include footwear, clothing, and accessories.

The badminton racket is an excellent option for players who are looking for a competitive badminton racket at a good price.

Is Li-Ning a good brand for badminton racket?

title: Babolat Shadow Team (Black/Blue) Badminton Shoes
description:
Babolat Shadow Team Badminton Shoes (Black/Blue) are designed for intense gameplay. Besides being more comfortable, the shoes have all the qualities which are required for optimal moves and stances. It perfectly meets the needs of long training sessions and repeated matches. Nothing will stop you. You can only take advantage if you are responsive and precise in your stances and moves.
Babolat has teamed up with Michelin to develop a special sole with remarkable performance: a three-dimensional grip combined with a unique rubber formula that guarantees explosive movements and controlled sudden stops without compromising on durability. The heel, which endures heavy strain, is protected by a bi-density sole that absorbs shocks and simultaneously helps you rebound. The shoe’s structure has been designed to support the foot for any type of stance; the upper material moulds the foot’s shape while preventing the foot from moving inside the shoe.
About Babolat: Founded in 1875 in Lyon, France, Babolat is the oldest racquet sports company in the world. Babolat products include racquets, strings, shoes, balls, shuttlecocks, bags, apparel, and accessories. They are designed and developed to allow every player to express their game.
Are the badminton shoes light or heavy?
The Babolat Shadow Team Badminton shoes are very light and provide stability.

title: Asics Gel Rocket 11 (White) Badminton Shoes
description: The Asics Gel Rocket 11 Badminton shoes is a multi-purpose indoor court shoe that comes with excellent cushioning. It features an engineered croslite upper that ensures to keep your feet relaxed and at ease throughout. Besides, this pair is durable, light in weight, and comfortable to wear. Designed with a TRUSSTIC application in the midsole, this application improves stability during quick transitions. Creating excellent comfort, the GEL technology cushioning unit in the heel is functional for providing better shock absorption. A wrap-up outsole and outrigger are functional support components during side-to-side movements. In contrast, the heel wrap-up expands the contact area during the landing phase of your stride to help generate a smoother landing. Lastly, the flexible grooves in the outsole complement a side grip design that improves flexibility on the court.

title: YONEX Aeroclub ACB TR Badminton Feather Shuttlecock (Pack of 10)
description:
YONEX Aeroclub ACB TR Feather Shuttlecock is manufactured to ensure the desired speed and consistency. It is extensively checked and tested, making it an ideal choice for tournaments. The shuttle is made of a natural cork base and a goose feather skirt. The YONEX Aeroclub TR feather shuttlecock is designed for practice and training games using composite cork and mixed feathers to create a good durable, and a smooth flying shuttlecock. The Aeroclub ACB TR feather shuttlecock is targeted for club/practice games at a super low economical price. Perfect for high-level club or tournament play. The Aeroclub ACB TR demonstrates excellent flight and durability for the price. Precision-manufactured to ensure the correct speed, distance, and stability performance in different temperatures and environments.
About YONEX: YONEX manufactures badminton racquets and other sports equipment. The company has been in business since 1968 and is known for its superior quality and attention to detail.
 How long does a Yonex Aeroclub ACB TR shuttle last?
